* Dynamic Views\nfor Access Control
** Extends standard views
***_ Row-level filters
***_ Column-level masks
** Based on user identity
***_ is_account_group_member() function
***_ CASE WHEN for conditional logic
** Column masking
***_ Redact sensitive columns for non-admins
***_ e.g., email → 'REDACTED'
** Row-level security
***_ WHERE clause with condition
***_ Restrict high-value rows to managers
** Requires SQL warehouse or compatible compute
@endmindmap
